NAME
====
netquery - the system introspection tool

DESCRIPTION
===========

The goal is to get a library with unified interface to introspect system:
* use GraphQL as the query language
* retrieve data in the JSON format.

DEVELOPMENT
===========

* One commit one change.
* Every single commit must produce buildable package.
* NetBSD code style (share/misc/style)
* Written in ANSI C99

GOALS
=====
* The primary goal is to write an introspection tool.
* Small-footprint.
* Portable across modern POSIX systems.
* Limit dependencies to GraphQL and JSON parsers.

